Springbok coach Rassie Erasmus and captain Siya Kolisi are holding their final media conference before the team departs for Japan. • Editor’s note: Livestream above courtesy DStv 403. You can also watch it on DStv Now. JOHANNESBURG - Springboks coach Rassie Erasmus and captain Siya Kolisi are holding the final media conference on Thursday before the team departs for Japan. WATCH: Springboks squad for #RWC2019 announced South Africa open their Rugby Championship campaign against New Zealand on 21 September. The event will also feature an address by the Minister of Sport Nathi Mthethwa.